# ============================================================
# CRITICAL SECURITY NOTE
# ============================================================
# .env is listed above and must NEVER be committed.
# This file would contain:
#   MODE=paper (safe)
#   DATABASE_URL (contains credentials)
# It must NOT contain:
#   EXCHANGE_API_KEY   (live trading — not supported in v1)
#   EXCHANGE_API_SECRET (live trading — not supported in v1)
